Shooter mechanism
Design

set ball loaded false

always
    spin flywheel slowly

when flywheel is unable to spin
    stop inhaling
    exhale slowly until wheel is able to spin
    set ball loaded true

on prefire
    fail if wheel is unable to spin
    fail if ball is unloaded
    rev up flywheel

on fire
    fail if wheel is not spinning fast enough
    inhale quickly for a half a second
    set ball loaded false

on inhale request
    inhale quickly

on exhale request
    exhale quickly
    set ball loaded false

states
    passive
    exhaling
    inhaling
    preloading
    loaded
    prefiring
    firing
    